<template>
  <a-layout>
    <a-layout-header>
      <div class="demo-logo" />
      <a-menu
        theme="dark"
        mode="horizontal"
        :defaultSelectedKeys="['2']"
        :items="items1"
        style="flex: 1; min-width: 0"
      />
    </a-layout-header>
    <a-layout-content style="padding: 0 48px">
      <a-breadcrumb style="margin: 16px 0">
        <a-breadcrumb-item>Home</a-breadcrumb-item>
        <a-breadcrumb-item>List</a-breadcrumb-item>
        <a-breadcrumb-item>App</a-breadcrumb-item>
      </a-breadcrumb>
      <a-layout
        style="padding: 24px 0; background: #1890ff; border-radius: 4px"
      >
        <a-sider style="background: #1890ff" width="200">
          <a-menu
            mode="inline"
            :defaultSelectedKeys="['1']"
            :defaultOpenKeys="['sub1']"
            style="height: 100%"
            :items="items2"
          />
        </a-sider>
        <a-layout-content style="padding: 0 24px; min-height: 280">
          Content
        </a-layout-content>
      </a-layout>
    </a-layout-content>
    <a-layout-footer style="text-align: center">
      Ant Design Â©{{ new Date().getFullYear() }} Created by Ant UED
    </a-layout-footer>
  </a-layout>
</template>

<script>
import {
  LaptopOutlined,
  NotificationOutlined,
  UserOutlined,
} from "@ant-design/icons-vue";
import { Breadcrumb, Layout, Menu } from "ant-design-vue";
import { defineComponent, ref } from "vue";

export default defineComponent({
  components: {
    "a-layout": Layout,
    "a-layout-header": Layout.Header,
    "a-layout-content": Layout.Content,
    "a-layout-footer": Layout.Footer,
    "a-breadcrumb": Breadcrumb,
    "a-breadcrumb-item": Breadcrumb.Item,
    "a-menu": Menu,
    "a-sider": Layout.Sider,
  },
  setup() {
    const items1 = ref(
      ["1", "2", "3"].map((key) => ({
        key,
        label: `nav ${key}`,
      }))
    );
    const items2 = ref(
      [UserOutlined, LaptopOutlined, NotificationOutlined].map(
        (icon, index) => {
          const key = String(index + 1);
          return {
            key: `sub${key}`,
            icon,
            label: `subnav ${key}`,
            children: Array(4)
              .fill(null)
              .map((_, j) => ({
                key: `${index * 4 + j + 1}`,
                label: `option${index * 4 + j + 1}`,
              })),
          };
        }
      )
    );
    return {
      items1,
      items2,
    };
  },
});
</script>

<style>
.demo-logo {
  /* Add your logo styles here */
}
</style>
